B.a06=new A.m(B.v,"\ud83d\udccb Standart Pozisyon Raporu Format\u0131",'**ICAO standart s\u0131ras\u0131:**\n1. **Aircraft identification** \u2014 u\xe7ak kimli\u011fi\n2. **Position** \u2014 mevcut nokta/fix\n3. **Time** \u2014 ge\xe7i\u015f zaman\u0131 (UTC)\n4. **Flight level / altitude** \u2014 y\xfckseklik\n5. **Next position** \u2014 sonraki nokta\n6. **Estimated time** \u2014 tahmini ge\xe7i\u015f zaman\u0131\n7. **Ensuing significant point** (iste\u011fe ba\u011fl\u0131) \u2014 sonraki \xf6nemli nokta\n\n**Yayg\u0131n ifadeler:**\n\u2022 "Over [fix]" \u2192 [nokta] \xfczerindeyiz\n\u2022 "Estimating [fix] at [time]" \u2192 [noktay\u0131] [zamanda] tahmin ediyoruz\n\u2022 "Abeam [fix]" \u2192 [noktan\u0131n] hizas\u0131nday\u0131z\n\u2022 "Passing [altitude]" \u2192 [y\xfcksekli\u011fi] ge\xe7iyoruz',null,null,null)
