B.a2e=new A.m(B.v,"U\xe7u\u015f Fazlar\u0131 ve Anahtar Terimler","**1. Pre-flight / Preflight**\n\u2014 walkaround, fuel check, NOTAMs, weight & balance\n\n**2. Taxi (Ground phase)**\n\u2014 taxiway, holding point, line up, backtrack\n\n**3. Takeoff**\n\u2014 rotate, V1 (decision speed), Vr (rotation speed), V2 (takeoff safety speed)\n\n**4. Climb (Departure)**\n\u2014 initial climb, SID, transition altitude, cruise climb\n\n**5. Cruise**\n\u2014 flight level, Mach number, step climb, drift down\n\n**6. Descent**\n\u2014 top of descent, STAR, speed restrictions\n\n**7. Approach**\n\u2014 ILS, localizer, glideslope, decision altitude (DA), MDA\n\n**8. Landing**\n\u2014 flare, touchdown, rollout, reverse thrust, exit vacate\n\n**9. Post-flight**\n\u2014 shutdown, parking, log entry, technical log",null,null,null)
