B.YM=new A.m(B.x,"\u0130leri kelime bilgisi iyiyi m\xfckemmelden ay\u0131r\u0131r","ICAO Seviye 5 ve 6 yeterli\u011fi, az kullan\u0131lan ancak y\xfcksek \xf6neme sahip teknik s\xf6zc\xfcklere hakim olmay\u0131 gerektirir. Bu ders, ileri d\xfczey adaylar\u0131 ay\u0131rt eden ve en zor s\u0131nav sorular\u0131nda s\u0131k\xe7a kar\u015f\u0131la\u015f\u0131lan terimleri kapsar.",null,null,null)
B.a0Y=new A.m(B.v,"\ud83c\udfc6 \u0130leri Operasyonel Terimler","**EDTO/ETOPS** \u2014 Extended Diversion Time Operations (flying far from alternate airports)\n**RVSM** \u2014 Reduced Vertical Separation Minima (300m / 1,000ft between FL290\u2013FL410)\n**PBN** \u2014 Performance-Based Navigation (RNP, RNAV specs)\n**MNPS** \u2014 Minimum Navigation Performance Specification (oceanic)\n**MEL** \u2014 Minimum Equipment List (approved deferred defects)\n**CDL** \u2014 Configuration Deviation List (approved structural deviations)\n**AOG** \u2014 Aircraft on Ground (urgent unserviceable aircraft)",null,null,null)
